                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable E</hi> 38.) On the 31st of March I saw the prisoner running down Great Russell-street, from the Prosecutor's shop, with a bundle under his arm—I stopped him, and asked what he had there—he threw the bundle down—I picked it up, and took him back to the prosecutor's shop, and he identified ten handkerchiefs which were in the bundle.</p>
