                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner</hi>. It was given into my hands by a carroty-headed young man <hi rend="italic">Witness</hi>. He was alone, and not ten yards from the shop when I stopped him—if there had been another young man I must have seen him, for I saw the prisoner come from the shop.</p>
